    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The Test conditions factor is one gradation below required due to single test condition; this gap is accepted given the Medium model risk level and the strong quantitative agreement observed across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, differences < 5%). The FEA framework is accepted for use in the non-cannulated pedicle screw 510(k) submission.",
